       fhir:Extension.valueMarkdown [ fhir:value "A primary series of 3 doses of DTP-containing vaccine is recommended, with the first \n  dose administered as early as 6 weeks of age. Subsequent doses should be given with an interval of at least 4 weeks between doses." ]
